these days.

128
00:12:17.779 --> 00:12:19.947
That's not fair. You know
I had to take time off.

129
00:12:19.948 --> 00:12:21.782
Well. it's not my fault
if you can't keep up.

130
00:12:21.783 --> 00:12:23.033
How are you going
to be a lawyer

131
00:12:23.034 --> 00:12:24.661
