a new path.

162
00:13:47.911 --> 00:13:51.164
Your reaction was
actually quite normal.

163
00:13:53.875 --> 00:13:55.001
Well. that's me!

164
00:13:56.378 --> 00:13:59.004
<i>Well. ahoy there. mateys!</i>

165
00:13:59.005 --> 00:14:01.298
<i>Tired of spending
